    "Hence, DRaFT-Q remains practical for 4-bit fine-tuning on consumer or mid-range GPUs.4 Experimental Setup Benchmarks and DatasetsTo comprehensively evaluate DRaFT-Q, we selected six diverse benchmarks: CommonsenseQA, OpenBookQA, GSM8K, OpenAssistant, OpenHermes, and UltraChat.",
    "These datasets span a wide range of reasoning challenges-from everyday commonsense inference to dialogue-based reasoning and multi-step symbolic problem solving.",
    "This diversity allows us to test the robustness of DRaFT-Q's rank adaptation and reward-weighted optimization mechanisms under varying task structures, supervision forms, and input complexities.CommonsenseQA contains five-way multiple-choice questions requiring implicit commonsense understanding beyond surface-level cues.",
    "OpenBookQA assesses scientific reasoning, demanding the integration of factual recall and logical inference.",
    "GSM8K consists of grade-school math word problems that require multi-step symbolic manipulation and exact numerical calculations."
